## Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)

**Can I connect MoEngage to WhatsApp without a developer?**
Yes, by using an AI platform that acts as an integration pipe, you can connect platforms like MoEngage or CleverTap to WhatsApp using simple webhook configurations that require zero coding.

**Do I need to approve every WhatsApp message template?**
Yes. Meta requires that all outbound marketing, utility, and authentication messages be pre-approved templates. Your AI pipe platform will help you manage and submit these templates for approval.

**What happens if a customer replies to the marketing message?**
If you integrate natively, the reply often goes to a dead inbox. By using an AI pipe like Chatzy AI, the conversational AI instantly takes over to answer the customer's questions, handle objections, or route them to a live support agent.

**Is WhatsApp marketing more expensive than SMS?**
WhatsApp conversation pricing varies by region and category (marketing vs. utility). While the upfront cost per message might be slightly higher than SMS in some regions, the return on investment (ROI) is exponentially higher due to the 98% open rates and interactive capabilities.

